7 Sec. 49. Section 84-1504, Revised Statutes Supplement, 2025, is
8 amended to read:
9 84-1504 (1) The Public Employees Retirement Board, on behalf of the
10 state, may contract with any individual to defer a portion of such
11 individual's compensation or with the Legislative Council to defer any
